get.summary: Find People in PipelineDeals account, using the provided CEQL search expression. The search expression in CEQL is the WHERE clause in a typical SQL query, but without the WHERE keyword. For example, to search for all People whose name contains the word 'jones', the search expression parameter will be person_name='%jones%'. If a search expression is not provided, then the first 30 people will be returned.
